Class Data3a

  • java.lang.Object
    • Data3a

  • public class Data3a
extends java.lang.Object
    Class for implementing initialized constants. The only constants in VSL are character strings. A label must be associated to its textual content and is used as the name of the text in three-address code. So the class is simple: it contains the label and its text.

    MLB
